*French: [[quel âge as-tu?]] (informal), [[quel âge avez-vous?]] (formal)
*Icelandic: 
:* [[hvað]] [[ertu]] [[gamall]]? (for males)
:* [[hvað]] [[ertu]] [[gömul]]? (for females)
