* Italian: [[Quanti anni hai?]] (informal), [[Quanti anni ha?]] (formal)
*Japanese: [[何歳ですか？]] (なんさいですか？, ''Nansai desu ka?'')
*Polish: [[ile masz lat?]]
*Russian: [[сколько вам лет?]]
*Swedish: [[hur gammal är du?]]
*Telugu: [[నీ వయసెంత?]] (nee vayaseMta?), [[మీ వయసెంత?]] (''respectful'': mee vayaseMta?)
